edu.uky.cepis.util.global

Class CEPISGlobalComponentConfigurator

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uky.cepis.util.global.CEPISConfigurator
      • edu.uky.cepis.util.global.CEPISGlobalComponentConfigurator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CEPISGlobalComponentConfigurator
extends CEPISConfigurator
    CEPISGlobalComponentConfigurator preloads the default CEPIS list fields such as AddressType, PhoneType, etc to avoid repeated database queries.
    This class uses the business/service layer objects to perform one-time fetch.
    This class extends CEPISConfigurator
    Author:
    keerthi
